detailLists: Media-based application used by NBCU employees for managing media-related requests.

The application allows users make request to create, download, delete, send, and move media
files, as well as initialize upcoming events.

It also features a dashboard for viewing and managing all requests submitted through the
portal.

Interactive Online Banking Application that supports User-Friendly Experience with fully
responsive design that allows easy access on any device, enabling effortless management of your
accounts.

Access a diverse range of services, including Business Loans, Personal Savings, Fixed-Term
Deposits (FTD), Non-Resident Accounts (NA), Educational Accounts (EA), and Educational
Institutional Savings Accounts (EAISA).

Online Medical Resource for Genentech Products designed for healthcare providers, offering
clinical and trial information on Genentech products through a web platform.

The portal Enables PIs to manage patient medical diaries and activities efficiently. Provides a
feature for scheduling virtual appointments with patients via video or audio calls
